question.title: Applet getting hang on Google Chrome

node.contents:
google chrome does not support 
<applet>
  tag - use 
 <object> tag instead. If u already r, ignore this comment</object>
</applet>

node.contents: When the page is load Applet, it will hang until I close it. Check the window task manager, I found if kill the Applet processor, the page won't be hang.I try to print some message on Applet init() and start(), but these messages does not show.Only I can do is get the full dump by JVM as follow. Could anyone tell me why Applet hangs before it started? Thanks for help.
